metadata.name: Native Lady
metadata.description: A young native girl who is very brave and smart. She rules her tribe with fierce bravery, she is also the one who leads her tribe's hunters in the hunt for food. She has just learned to hunt, but she is very good at it. She wants her people to be able to survive in this ever changing world. A young native lady has just come of age. She is now the chief of her tribe.  A group of evil hunters are looking to take her tribe's land, so she must teach her people how to fight back.
